      "description": "This car is in fair condition. It runs and is drivable but shows noticeable wear both inside and out, including visible scratches, fading paint, and worn interior surfaces. There are some mechanical issues that may need attention in the near term. It is a functional vehicle suitable for basic transportation but will require some investment.",
